  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will use their fantastic skills to navigate mazes, forests, and avenues. Players can also interact and discover the towns folk NPCs and have meaningful close-up conversations with each and every single one of them. Players must also engage in difficult parkour situations within levels to progress within the seemingly ever growing story. <i>Voice work by the critically acclaimed TjMike310509.</i> <i>The game contains certain disturbing character depictions and drug references</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3545310/extras/ba1dcab1000ef629edb5a940c24c7eef.avif?t=1745453768\" width=444 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i><u>PLEASE</u></i><u> <i>NOTE:</i></u></strong><i> THE GAME IS STILL IN IT'S DEVELOPMENTAL PROCESS WE HERE AT MISERYOUS GAMES PLAN TO CONTINUE TO RELEASE NEW CONTENT UPDATES TO FURTHER THE STORY/GAMEPLAY ELEMENTS.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3545310/extras/683dfbcdf78cebc2f377dd0efd3ec938.avif?t=1745453768\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3545310/extras_big/683dfbcdf78cebc2f377dd0efd3ec938.avif?t=1745453768 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
